@page "/"

<PageTitle>IT Partners Directory | UIUC</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to the IT Partners Directory</h1>

<OfficeAdmin></OfficeAdmin>

<p>The IT Partners Directory is for faculty and staff to enter directory information for units, offices, and profiles. The information within the IT Partners Directory may be displayed on both your unit and office directories, as well as the UIUC Tech Help Center Help Desks page.</p>

<p>Some information can be updated at the campus level in the Illinois Directory. The IT Partners Directory will pull that information and most of it can also be updated in the IT Partners Directory.</p>

<div class="iled-card-list">
    @if (FullSecurityItem?.HasProfile ?? false)
    {
        <il-card class="il-theme-gray">
            <h2>Edit My Profile</h2>
            <p>You have a profile. Edit or preview your directory profile</p>
            <div class="iled-buttons">
                <a href="/profile/general" class="il-button">Edit</a>
                <ViewProfile></ViewProfile>
            </div>
        </il-card>
    }
    @if (FullSecurityItem?.IsAnyAdmin ?? false)
    {
        <il-card class="il-theme-gray">
            <h2>Office Administration</h2>
            <p>You are an office administrator. Edit those in your office and office information, including office location, hours, and contact information.</p>
            <div class="iled-buttons">
                <a href="/office/people" class="il-button">Edit People</a>
                <a href="/office/hours" class="il-button">Edit Office Hours</a>
            </div>
        </il-card>
    }
    <il-card class="il-theme-gray">
        <h2>Find an Administrator</h2>
        <p>If you find incorrect information about an office, you can view a list of office/unit administrators and their contact information.</p>
        <div class="iled-buttons">
            <a href="/search/offices" class="il-button">Office Admins</a>
            <a href="/search/units" class="il-button">Unit Admins</a>
        </div>
    </il-card>
</div>